In article <4075@bigfoot.first.gmd.de>, guest@g386bsd.first.gmd.de (A Guest) writes...
>Anyone have any information on the Purdy implemtation of DES?
>Specifically the Purdy-S type..  Please post to this newsgroup.
>i
